data.description: Welcome to your dream oasis in Maricopa! Spacious single-story pool home, situated on a private oversized cul-de-sac lot. Extended full-length patio overlooks the pool, waterfall feature, tiki-bar and outdoor storage. Vaulted ceilings, a chef's large kitchen island, upgraded maple cabinets, Tuscan travertine backsplash, walk-in pantry, and Whirlpool stainless appliances. Master suite boasts a generously sized walk-in closet, large bathroom with separate shower, Tuscan travertine soaking tub, & sliding door access to the back yard. 4th bedroom/den/office, features French doors, & walk-in closet. Home includes a full home water softener, built-in storage closets in the garage, recently painted exterior, new AC and porcelain tile throughout. Home has paid solar. Utilities average $70/month.
